overview.en: LOGISTICS (LGC) is a project that applies 4th generation blockchain technology to the traditional LOGISTICS industry, using a series of sophisticated algorithms, LGC's smart contracts will accurately record and Real-time updates of information.
overview.zh: LOGISTICS（LGC）是一个将第四代区块链技术应用于传统LOGISTICS行业的项目，它使用一系列复杂的算法，LGC的智能合约将准确记录和实时更新信息。
